high_descs: Walk forward until you're even with the dishwasher to your left and when you are turn left and walk to the dishwasher.
Pick up the knife that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the counter then turn left.
Cut the potato that's in front of you into slices.
Put the knife up near the sliced up potato.
Pick up a slice of potato from the sliced up potato that's in front of you.
Take a couple steps to your left until you're in front of the microwave.
Cook the slice of potato in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Take a step to your left then a small step backwards.
Put the slice of tomato somewhere out of sight.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of potato on the counter?

high_descs: Go to the counter above the dishwasher
Pick up a knife
Go slightly to the right
Cut the potato on the shelf
Put the knife down on the shelf
Pick up a potato slice
Go to the microwave
Heat the potato
Go to the bin on the left
Put the potato in the bin
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato slice in a bin

high_descs: Move straight, and when you get close to the stove, turn left and continue to the dishwasher.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter above the dishwasher.
Move a couple steps to your right to stand at the counter lined up with a blue pen.
Use the knife to slice the potato on the elevated counter behind the pen.
Stand the knife up on the counter in front of the potato.
Pick up the end slice of the potato.
Carry the potato slice to the microwave, which is just left of the dishwasher.
Place the potato slice in the microwave and then remove once heated.
Move slightly left to stand at the end of the counter by the trash bin while carrying the potato slice.
Place the potato slice in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a heated slice of potato.
